Package: MCMCDiag
Title: MCMC Convergence Diagnostics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Abin Alikunju", email = "alikunabin@myvuw.ac.nz", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for assessing convergence of Markov Chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) simulations.
    Implements Gelman-Rubin diagnostics, trace plots, and other convergence assessment methods.
